room_title: Escape room "The Games Room" by Code Stat Escape Rooms in Ventura
room_address: 3875 Telegraph Rd Suite D Ventura, CA 93003
room_description: Ladies and gentlemen, if you dare, enter this mid-twentieth-century exclusive late-night club and games room. Looking for merriment, you'll instead find a murder mystery on your hands. If you choose to pursue the killer—picking up the case where the last detective left off—the fate of the investigation will rest entirely on you.
